.cs 7 on
.item 'SHOW VMESSAGE Command' 'Added on 07/08/82 by LSO'
.boxon
SHOW VMESSAGE
.boxoff

.* DESCRIPTION
Required Privileges:  ???

The SHOW VMESSAGE (or SHOW VMSG) command displays the current VIEW message.
This message is also displayed via the SHOW VMESSAGE command.  The response
"No View message", is issued if there is no VIEW message.
.cs 7 off
